From 833e329588503ecc1ef304fb9538b045465be191 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Varun Nagalla <nagal@vcimagesorting>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 03:47:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] v1.1.0: dark navy/cyan/violet redesign + raise PC limit to
 500
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Raise Windows/desktop batch import limit from 200 → 500 photos
- Keep iPad/iPhone limit at 100 (memory safety)
- Update all UI text, docs, and in-app messages to reflect new limits
- Full visual redesign: dark navy #07090f background, cyan/teal/sky/
  indigo/violet gradient system matching VC reference icon
- Redesigned: topbar, brand mark (inline SVG VC), hero section,
  showcase cards, purpose cards, drop zone, filter chips, view tabs,
  photo grid, score badges, analysis overlay, modal, toast, footer
- Replaced all red/coral accent with teal→violet gradient
- New icon set: icon.svg, icon-192.png, icon-512.png,
  icon-512-maskable.png, apple-touch-icon.png, favicon-16/32.png,
  icon.ico (16/24/32/48/64/256px multi-size)
- PWA manifest: dark background_color/theme_color, split maskable icon
- Service worker v2 cache with updated asset list
- CSS version bump v8→v9, JS version bump v9→v10
- npm audit: 0 known vulnerabilities
- JS syntax check: PASS
- All 38 JS-toggled CSS classes verified present
- All security controls unchanged (CSP, no remote fonts/scripts)
- Copyright 2026 Varun Nagalla preserved

© 2026 Varun Nagalla. All Rights Reserved.
